        Powerful features to help your team stay organized and productive
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid"
      style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem"
    >
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="card" style="padding: 1.5rem">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
          <div
            style="
              width: 3rem;
              height: 3rem;
              border-radius: 0.5rem;
              background: #dbeafe;
              display: flex;
              align-items: center;
              justify-content: center;
            "
          >
            <svg
              class="icon-md"
              style="color: #2563eb"
